project.name: SamLearnsAzure
project.description:
There are 3 main goals of this project, focused on building infrastructure, developing features, and using monitoring to generate feedback 
- Infrastructure: using Azure, create a secure, scalable, and reliable web solution: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/architecture/reference-architectures/app-service-web-app/multi-region
- Development: using Azure DevOps, create a workflow to streamline the delivery of value to end users, using tracking, development, and testing: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/architecture/example-scenario/apps/devops-dotnet-webapp
- Feedback: using Azure Monitor, create a series of dashboards and alerts to understand bottlenecks, discover and debug issues and learn from user actions: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/architecture/reference-architectures/app-service-web-app/app-monitoring

You can follow the blog at https://SamLearnsAzure.blog
You can view the product at https://SamLearnsAzure.com
